Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHOOLHOUSE. Marine schoolhouse-in-a-box.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,PME today is three disconnected systems and a tired NCO. We fold them\Ninto one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Four datasets. Three use cases. One on-prem stack. Three role-aware\Nviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch to the student view — start with an egocentric tactical drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Multimodal coach reads the helmet-cam frame plus the Marine's typed\Naction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch drill — Visual ID. Drop a foreign platform image.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Vision-language analyst writes the numbered reasoning. SENTINEL\Npattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch drill — Written assignment. Logistics principles paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,chat_json grades each rubric criterion. 0-5 score plus narrative\Nfeedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch role — Instructor. Same data, reshaped — cohort heatmap\Nappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cache-first Schoolhouse Intelligence Brief. Anchored to NAVMC 3500.58.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch role — School CO. Same brief reshapes to a schoolhouse health\Ndashboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Audit chain — every drill, every brief, SHA-256 chained. Privacy Act\Ngoverned, not FERPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL — PME data stays inside the SCIF.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
